A stock 1600 SP can snap a tranny in two also.
http://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/index.mv?photo+55183.jpg
Not so much the size of the engine but what gets rgb trannies is wheel hop.
The force of the ring and pinion is greater then the case can handle when
the tire gets traction after returning to the ground.

